---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About The Hackney | 1856 Brewery Wedding & Events Venue, East London E2" description="The Hackney is a restored 1856 brewery on Hackney Road, East London. One team runs everything - weddings, events, cafe-bar and in-house kitchen. Meet the team behind the venue.">
<!-- ==================== NAVIGATION ==================== -->
  

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 1: HERO ==================== -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" role="img" aria-label="The Hackney venue interior showing exposed brick and industrial character"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="eyebrow">About The Hackney</div>
        <h1>An 1856 Brewery. One Team. Every Detail.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">We are a wedding and events venue, a cafe-bar, and an in-house kitchen - all under one roof, all run by one team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 2: THE BUILDING ==================== -->
  <section class="building fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="building-inner">
        <div class="building-text">
          <div class="section-label">The Building</div>
          <h2>A Victorian Brewery On Hackney Road</h2>
          <p>The Hackney sits at 503 Hackney Road, in a building that dates back to 1856. It started life as a Victorian brewery - and you can still see that history in the bones of the space. Exposed brick walls, original timber beams, high ceilings, and skylights that flood the room with natural light.</p>
          <p>When we restored the building, we kept the industrial character and added modern hospitality. The result is a venue with real warmth and texture - not a blank-canvas warehouse that needs dressing up, but a space that photographs beautifully as it is.</p>
          <p>We are right between Bethnal Green and Cambridge Heath, in the heart of East London. Two minutes from Cambridge Heath Overground, eight minutes from Bethnal Green on the Central line. Buses stop directly outside.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="building-images">
          <div class="building-placeholder lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="The Hackney building exterior on Hackney Road"></div>
          <div class="building-placeholder lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="Interior detail showing exposed brick and timber beams"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 3: ONE TEAM ==================== -->
  <section class="one-team fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="one-team-inner">
        <div class="section-label">How We Work</div>
        <h2>One Team. Not Twenty Vendors.</h2>
        <p>Most event venues hand you a list of approved suppliers and wish you luck. You end up coordinating a caterer, a florist, a bar team, a DJ, a coordinator - each with their own timeline, their own invoice, and their own idea of how your day should run.</p>
        <p>We do it differently.</p>
        <p>At The Hackney, everything is in-house. Our kitchen prepares your menu. Our bar team pours your drinks. Our events team plans your day. Our coordinator runs it on the morning. One team who know the building, know each other, and know exactly how to make your event feel effortless.</p>
        <p>This is not just about convenience - it is about quality. When the same team handles everything, nothing falls through the cracks. No miscommunication between suppliers. No surprise invoices. No chasing five different people the week before your event.</p>

        <div class="one-team-callout">
          <p>The price we quote is the price you pay. One invoice, one team, no surprises.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 4: MEET THE TEAM ==================== -->
  <section class="team fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="team-header">
        <div class="section-label">The People</div>
        <h2>Meet The Team</h2>
        <p>The people who make it happen - from your first enquiry to the last dance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center top" role="img" aria-label="Jon Penn - Director of The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="team-name">Jon Penn</div>
          <div class="team-role">Director</div>
          <p class="team-bio">Co-founder and owner of The Hackney. Jon oversees the business and drives the vision for the venue.</p>
          <a href="https://jonspenn.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="team-link">jonspenn.com &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center top" role="img" aria-label="James - Director of The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="team-name">James</div>
          <div class="team-role">Director</div>
          <p class="team-bio">Co-founder and director. James works behind the scenes to keep the business running.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center top" role="img" aria-label="Hugo - General Manager at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="team-name">Hugo</div>
          <div class="team-role">General Manager</div>
          <p class="team-bio">Hugo is your first point of contact. He runs every venue tour, handles enquiries, and makes sure your event runs perfectly from start to finish.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center top" role="img" aria-label="Eva - Events Manager at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="team-name">Eva</div>
          <div class="team-role">Events Manager</div>
          <p class="team-bio">Eva manages the planning process from booking to the big day. She coordinates every detail so you do not have to.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center top" role="img" aria-label="Chef Marco Mannoni - Head Chef at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="team-name">Chef Marco Mannoni</div>
          <div class="team-role">Head Chef</div>
          <p class="team-bio">Marco leads our in-house kitchen. Modern European cuisine, seasonal menus, locally sourced ingredients. From exquisitely plated courses to abundant sharing feasts, every dish is designed to bring people together over beautifully crafted plates.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="The kitchen and bar team at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="team-name">The Kitchen & Bar Team</div>
          <div class="team-role">The People Behind Every Course & Cocktail</div>
          <p class="team-bio">Every coffee, cocktail, and course is made by our team - all employed by The Hackney, not outsourced. The same people who serve your morning flat white are the ones pouring champagne at your wedding.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 5: VENUE GALLERY ==================== -->
  <section class="venue-gallery fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="venue-gallery-header">
        <div class="section-label">The Venue</div>
        <h2>The Space</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <div class="gallery-item-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="The main space at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">The Main Space</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <div class="gallery-item-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="The bar at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">The Bar</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <div class="gallery-item-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="The winter garden at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">The Winter Garden</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <div class="gallery-item-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="The courtyard terrace at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">The Courtyard</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <div class="gallery-item-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="Ceremony setup at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">Ceremony Setup</div>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <div class="gallery-item-bg lazy-bg" data-bg="" data-bg-pos="center center" role="img" aria-label="Evening celebration mode at The Hackney"></div>
          <div class="gallery-caption">Evening Mode</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 6: PRESS & RECOGNITION ==================== -->
  <section class="press fade-in">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="press-inner">
        <div class="section-label">The Numbers</div>
        <h2>Trusted By Hundreds Of Couples</h2>

        <div class="press-stats">
          <div class="press-stat">
            <div class="press-stat-number">4.6</div>
            <div class="press-stat-label">Google rating (633 reviews)</div>
          </div>
          <div class="press-stat">
            <div class="press-stat-number">98</div>
            <div class="press-stat-label">NPS score - 98% would recommend</div>
          </div>
          <div class="press-stat">
            <div class="press-stat-number">75+</div>
            <div class="press-stat-label">Weddings a year</div>
          </div>
          <div class="press-stat">
            <div class="press-stat-number">Est. 1856</div>
            <div class="press-stat-label">A historic brewery, reimagined</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="press-badges">
          <span class="press-badge">Hitched</span>
          <span class="press-badge">Bridebook</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== SECTION 7: FINAL CTA ==================== -->
  <section class="final-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">Come And See Us</div>
      <h2>Ready To See The Space?</h2>
      <p class="final-cta-body">Whether you are planning a wedding, an event, or just want a great coffee - we would love to welcome you.</p>
      <div class="final-cta-buttons">
        <a href="/check-your-date/?utm_source=website&utm_medium=cta&utm_campaign=about" class="btn btn-primary">Check Your Date</a>
        <a href="/cafe-bar/" class="btn btn-outline">Visit The Cafe</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ==================== FOOTER ==================== -->
  

  <!-- ==================== JAVASCRIPT ==================== -->

<style is:global>
    /* ==================== PAGE-SPECIFIC STYLES ==================== */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 100px 0 80px;
    }

    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: var(--forest-olive);
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .hero .container { width: 100%; }

    .eyebrow {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--dusty-coral);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    /* ==================== THE BUILDING ==================== */
    .building {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }

    .building-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .building-text h2 {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .building-text p {
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .building-images {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .building-placeholder {
      aspect-ratio: 16/10;
      background: #3D2117;
    }

    .building-placeholder:nth-child(2) { background: #4A3228; }

    /* ==================== ONE TEAM ==================== */
    .one-team {
      padding: 100px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(44,24,16,0.06);
    }

    .one-team-inner {
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .one-team h2 {
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .one-team p {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .one-team-callout {
      background: rgba(44,24,16,0.03);
      padding: 36px 40px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--fired-brick);
      margin-top: 36px;
    }

    .one-team-callout p {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 22px;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      color: var(--brewery-dark);
    }

    /* ==================== MEET THE TEAM ==================== */
    .team {
      padding: 100px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(44,24,16,0.06);
    }

    .team-header {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .team-header h2 {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .team-header p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .team-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 32px;
    }

    .team-card {}

    .team-photo {
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      background: #3D2117;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .team-card:nth-child(2) .team-photo { background: var(--forest-olive); }
    .team-card:nth-child(3) .team-photo { background: #4A3228; }
    .team-card:nth-child(4) .team-photo { background: #5C3A1E; }
    .team-card:nth-child(5) .team-photo { background: var(--fired-brick); }
    .team-card:nth-child(6) .team-photo { background: #3A5C1E; }

    .team-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--fired-brick);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .team-link:hover { color: var(--brewery-dark); }

    .team-name {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .team-role {
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--dusty-coral);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .team-bio {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .team-bio .placeholder {
      color: var(--fired-brick);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* ==================== VENUE GALLERY ==================== */
    .venue-gallery {
      padding: 100px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(44,24,16,0.06);
    }

    .venue-gallery-header {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .venue-gallery-header h2 {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .gallery-item {
      position: relative;
      aspect-ratio: 16/10;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .gallery-item-bg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: #3D2117;
    }

    .gallery-item:nth-child(2) .gallery-item-bg { background: var(--forest-olive); }
    .gallery-item:nth-child(3) .gallery-item-bg { background: #4A3228; }
    .gallery-item:nth-child(4) .gallery-item-bg { background: #5C3A1E; }
    .gallery-item:nth-child(5) .gallery-item-bg { background: #2E4009; }
    .gallery-item:nth-child(6) .gallery-item-bg { background: #3D2117; }

    .gallery-caption {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 16px;
      left: 16px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* ==================== PRESS & RECOGNITION ==================== */
    .press {
      padding: 80px 0;
      background: rgba(44,24,16,0.03);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(44,24,16,0.06);
    }

    .press-inner {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .press h2 {
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .press-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .press-stat-number {
      font-family: var(--font-heading);
      font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brewery-dark);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .press-stat-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--dusty-coral);
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .press-badges {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .press-badge {
      background: rgba(44,24,16,0.06);
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--brewery-dark);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-weight: 500;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    /* ==================== FINAL CTA ==================== */
    .final-cta {
      background: var(--brewery-dark);
      padding: 80px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .final-cta h2 {
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .final-cta-body {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 540px;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
    }

    .final-cta-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    /* ==================== SCROLL ANIMATIONS ==================== */
    .fade-in {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }

    .fade-in.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ==================== RESPONSIVE ==================== */
    @media (max-width: 1200px) {
      .team-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .press-stats {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .building-inner {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 36px;
      }

      .team-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
      }

      .gallery-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .final-cta-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .one-team-callout {
        padding: 28px;
      }

      body {
        padding-bottom: 52px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Base>
